    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Flat surfaces or slabs, either portable or mounted on a wall or other structure, bearing or intended to bear inscriptions or pictures; also, thin, rigid slabs used as writing surfaces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000025091/Harrod's Librarians' Glossary (1995)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Superficies planas o tabletas, portátiles o colocadas en una pared u otra estructura, que tienen o destinadas a tener inscripciones o ilustraciones; también, tabletas rígidas delgadas usadas como superficies para escribir.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
